'''''Yavin's Glory''''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] patrol cruiser. Its crew once happened upon an abandoned [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] vessel which had been attacked by the [[Red Moons]] group. The Red Moons had used the chemical [[DX-343]] to force the Imperials to abandon ship.

